{"ts":"2026-06-27T05:40:58.243Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Reviewing Initial Code**\n\nI'm thrilled with the absence of compilation errors, a fantastic start! Now, I'm diving into `app/admin/clients/[id]/page.tsx` to craft a stellar client audit page. I am re-examining the contents of this file and starting with a comprehensive code review.\n\n\n**Designing Client Audit Page**\n\nI'm now designing the layout for the client audit page, aiming for a comprehensive view. I'm focusing on integrating mock data to accurately represent the selected client's information. I have reviewed the mock data model, and have taken note of the following data points: `id`, `name`, `domain`, `status`, `tier`, `createdAt`, `region`, `complianceLevel`, `contactName`, and `contactEmail`, and the enriched admin telemetry: `industry`, `accountOwner`, `billingStatus`, and `healthStatus`.\n\n\n**Refining Data Lookup**\n\nI've refined the data lookup to enrich client information, matching the list page logic. Now, I'm integrating operational values directly within the conditional statements based on `clientObj.id`. I'm incorporating detailed operational values such as industry, health status, billing status, and account owner for client-specific context.\n\n\n**Integrating Client Details**\n\nI'm now integrating detailed operational values for specific clients. I am using conditional statements based on `clientObj.id` to include relevant details such as industry, health status, billing status, and account owner for client-specific context. I've enriched the `clientObj` with mock data, so each client has enriched data. I'm also now implementing the functions to fetch the related projects and agent operations for the client.\n\n\n**Designing Visual Assets**\n\nI am now designing the visual assets for the client detail page, aiming to select at least four premium elements from the UI Quality Constitution. Currently, I'm leaning toward an interactive tabs and selector system, narrative timeline, secure portal preview, and bento grid. I am also considering a carousel or horizontal story rail, or possibly a knowledge graph visual, depending on how best to represent data from `@/lib/mock-data-model`.\n\n\n**Prioritizing Visual Elements**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the visual assets. I've decided to prioritize the listed elements for the client detail page, envisioning a cohesive Apple-like design. I am going to build out the sections of the page in more detail to ensure a visually premium experience. I am particularly excited about the potential of the SVG/CSS architecture graphic and the interactive controls panel.\n\n\n**Defining Visual Structure**\n\nI am now structuring the visual elements, focusing on a clean, GFF-consistent design. I'm prioritizing avoiding box clutter, with a monochrome dark backdrop and electric-blue, teal/emerald, and soft-amber accents. I've curated a list of essential icons from `lucide-react`, like `ArrowLeft`, `Shield`, and `Clock`, to keep the UI slick. I'm now drafting the code for `app/admin/clients/[id]/page.tsx`, envisioning a CSS rotating enclave shield and active key-exchange paths within an SVG graphic. I'm thinking of a pulsing double-shield graphic with an SVG grid pattern.\n\n\n**Constructing Security Graphic**\n\nI'm now building a zero-dependency SVG/CSS graphic. It'll feature a ring representing the \"Sovereign HSM Boundary.\" Pulsing connections will radiate to three nodes: secure kernel, multi-agent lattices, and attestation ledger. An animated CSS path will simulate TLS key-exchanges. This custom graphic will be premium.\n\nI'm also working on the Narrative Timeline. I've completed the PKI Handshake Protocol, eBPF Kernel Boundaries, and Guardrail Alignment Scan stages. Now I'm focused on the Attestation Log Ledger, which will be live-polling. The Bento Grid is next.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T05:40:58.270Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"b5kakf6o","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/clients/[id]/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport { useParams, useRouter } from \"next/navigation\";\nimport { \n  ArrowLeft, Shield, ShieldCheck, Cpu, Clock, CreditCard, Layers, \n  Bot, Activity, HardDrive, Terminal, RefreshCw, AlertTriangle, \n  CheckCircle2, Lock, Settings2, ExternalLink, FileText, Users, BadgeCheck\n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport { \n  previewClientAccounts, \n  previewProjects, \n  previewAgentOperations,\n  ClientAccount,\n  Project,\n  AgentOperation\n} from \"@/lib/mock-data-model\";\n\n// Extended interface matching the clients page\ninterface EnrichedClient extends ClientAccount {\n  industry: string;\n  accountOwner: string;\n  billingStatus: \"Paid\" | \"Unpaid\" | \"Processing\" | \"Overdue\";\n  healthStatus: \"Healthy\" | \"Warning\" | \"Critical\" | \"Offline\";\n}\n\nexport default function AdminClientDetailPage() {\n  const router = useRouter();\n  const { id } = useParams();\n\n  const clientId = typeof id === \"string\" ? id : \"client-001\";\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 1. DATA LOOKUP & ENRICHMENT\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const rawClient = previewClientAccounts.find(c => c.id === clientId) || previewClientAccounts[0];\n\n  // Enrich data mirroring the master registry\n  const getEnrichedClient = (c: ClientAccount): EnrichedClient => {\n    let industry = \"Cybersecurity & Defense\";\n    let healthStatus: \"Healthy\" | \"Warning\" | \"Critical\" | \"Offline\" = \"Healthy\";\n    let billingStatus: \"Paid\" | \"Unpaid\" | \"Processing\" | \"Overdue\" = \"Paid\";\n    let accountOwner = \"Dr. Sarah Vance\";\n\n    if (c.id === \"client-001\") {\n      industry = \"Cybersecurity & Defense\";\n      healthStatus = \"Healthy\";\n      billingStatus = \"Paid\";\n      accountOwner = \"Dr. Sarah Vance\";\n    } else if (c.id === \"client-002\") {\n      industry = \"E-Commerce & Retail\";\n      healthStatus = \"Warning\";\n      billingStatus = \"Overdue\";\n      accountOwner = \"Alexander Mercer\";\n    } else if (c.id === \"client-003\") {\n      industry = \"Supply Chain & Logistics\";\n      healthStatus = \"Offline\";\n      billingStatus = \"Unpaid\";\n      accountOwner = \"Sarah Jenkins\";\n    } else if (c.id === \"client-004\") {\n      industry = \"FinTech & Treasury\";\n      healthStatus = \"Healthy\";\n      billingStatus = \"Paid\";\n      accountOwner = \"Marcus Vance\";\n    }\n\n    return {\n      ...c,\n      industry,\n      healthStatus,\n      billingStatus,\n      accountOwner\n    };\n  };\n\n  const client = getEnrichedClient(rawClient);\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 2. CHILD PROJECTS & AGENTS CORRELATION\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const clientProjects = previewProjects.filter(p => p.clientAccountId === client.id);\n  const projectIds = clientProjects.map(p => p.id);\n  const clientAgents = previewAgentOperations.filter(op => projectIds.includes(op.projectId));\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 3. PAGE TABS & INTERACTION\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<\"telemetry\" | \"architecture\" | \"compliance\" | \"workloads\">(\"telemetry\");\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 4. ACTION SIMULATION STATE (ROTATING KEYS, AUDITS)\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  const [isRotatingKey, setIsRotatingKey] = useState(false);\n  const [isScanning, setIsScanning] = useState(false);\n  const [consoleLogs, setConsoleLogs] = useState<string[]>([\n    `[${new Date().toISOString().split(\"T\")[1].slice(0, 8)}] ADMIN_INIT: Administrative oversight session opened by Dr. Sarah Vance`,\n    `[${new Date().toISOString().split(\"T\")[1].slice(0, 8)}] SECURE_LINK: TLS 1.3 socket bound to Sovereign partition namespace: ${client.domain}`,\n    `[${new Date().toISOString().split(\"T\")[1].slice(0, 8)}] ATTESTATION: Root HSM state verified. Seal ID: SHA-0x${client.id.toUpperCase()}`\n  ]);\n\n  const addConsoleLog = (text: string) => {\n    const timestamp = new Date().toISOString().split(\"T\")[1].slice(0, 8);\n    setConsoleLogs(prev => [...prev, `[${timestamp}] ${text}`]);\n  };\n\n  const handleRotateHSMSeal = () => {\n    if (isRotatingKey || isScanning) return;\n    setIsRotatingKey(true);\n    addConsoleLog(\"HSM_KEY_ROLLOVER: Initiated ephemeral root seal rotation.\");\n    \n    setTimeout(() => {\n      addConsoleLog(\"HSM_KEY_ROLLOVER: [STEP 1] Generating fresh 4096-bit NTRU cryptographic parameters.\");\n      \n      setTimeout(() => {\n        addConsoleLog(\"HSM_KEY_ROLLOVER: [STEP 2] Signing new attestation key using administrative airgapped master vault.\");\n        \n        setTimeout(() => {\n          addConsoleLog(\"HSM_KEY_ROLLOVER: [STEP 3] Re-encapsulating secure memory spaces. Syncing with eBPF hooks.\");\n          \n          setTimeout(() => {\n            addConsoleLog(\"HSM_KEY_ROLLOVER: SUCCESS - Sovereign partition HSM rotated. New Seal ID generated: SHA-0x8A12FFCE\");\n            setIsRotatingKey(false);\n          }, 800);\n        }, 700);\n      }, 600);\n    }, 500);\n  };\n\n  const handleRunSecurityScan = () => {\n    if (isRotatingKey || isScanning) return;\n    setIsScanning(true);\n    addConsoleLog(\"COMPLIANCE_SCAN: Initiating continuous eBPF zero-trust kernel namespace compliance verification.\");\n    \n    setTimeout(() => {\n      addConsoleLog(\"COMPLIANCE_SCAN: [RUNNING] Scrutinizing network sockets... TLS 1.3 decapsulation state looks intact.\");\n      \n      setTimeout(() => {\n        addConsoleLog(\"COMPLIANCE_SCAN: [RUNNING] Checking Intel SGX / AMD SEV boundary memory maps against root policy.\");\n        \n        setTimeout(() => {\n          addConsoleLog(\"COMPLIANCE_SCAN: [RUNNING] Inspecting multi-agent sandbox execution rings and alignment ledger.\");\n          \n          setTimeout(() => {\n            addConsoleLog(`COMPLIANCE_SCAN: COMPLETED - Tenant isolation level is optimal. Compliance certified: ${client.complianceLevel}`);\n            setIsScanning(false);\n          }, 800);\n        }, 700);\n      }, 600);\n    }, 500);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n      \n      {/* HEADER BAR */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-5\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n          <button\n            onClick={() => router.push(\"/admin/clients\")}\n            className=\"p-1.5 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/50 hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n            aria-label=\"Back to tenant registry\"\n          >\n            <ArrowLeft className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n          </button>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                Administrative Oversight\n              </span>\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-white/30\">\n                {client.id.toUpperCase()}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono uppercase mt-1 flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n              <span>{client.name.replace(\" [Preview Client]\", \"\")}</span>\n              {client.tier === \"Sovereign\" && <BadgeCheck className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-400\" />}\n            </h2>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Live Status indicator */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs\">\n          <div className=\"p-2 rounded bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase text-[10px]\">Health:</span>\n            <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-bold ${\n              client.healthStatus === \"Healthy\" ? \"text-emerald-400\" :\n              client.healthStatus === \"Warning\" ? \"text-amber-400\" :\n              client.healthStatus === \"Critical\" ? \"text-red-400\" : \"text-white/30\"\n            }`}>\n              <span className={`h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-current ${client.healthStatus === \"Healthy\" || client.healthStatus === \"Warning\" ? \"animate-pulse\" : \"\"}`} />\n              {client.healthStatus.toUpperCase()}\n            </span>\n          </div>\n\n          <button\n            onClick={() => {\n              const customSession = {\n                name: client.contactName,\n                email: client.contactEmail,\n                role: \"client_admin\",\n                clearance: \"CLEARANCE LEVEL III (SANDBOX ADMIN)\",\n                isMock: true,\n                label: `PORTAL PREVIEW - ${client.name.toUpperCase()}`\n              };\n              localStorage.setItem(\"gff_ai_preview_session_v1\", JSON.stringify(customSession));\n              window.dispatchEvent(new Event(\"gff_preview_session_changed\"));\n              router.push(\"/portal/dashboard\");\n            }}\n            className=\"h-8 px-3 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase text-white flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer border-none\"\n          >\n            <ExternalLink className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n            <span>Mirror Portal</span>\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* DETAILED LAYOUT */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        \n        {/* LEFT COLUMN: ACTIVE VIEW MODULES */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 space-y-6\">\n          \n          {/* INTERACTIVE NAVIGATION TABS */}\n          <div className=\"flex border-b border-white/5 font-mono text-[11px] gap-1 bg-black/20 p-1 rounded-lg\">\n            {([\"telemetry\", \"architecture\", \"compliance\", \"workloads\"] as const).map((tab) => (\n              <button\n                key={tab}\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab)}\n                className={`flex-1 py-2 rounded-md font-bold uppercase transition-all text-center cursor-pointer border-none ${\n                  activeTab === tab \n                    ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-white border border-[#009DFF]/20\" \n                    : \"bg-transparent text-white/40 hover:text-white/70 hover:bg-white/[0.01] border border-transparent\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                {tab}\n              </button>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n\n          {/* TAB CONTENT: OPERATIONAL TELEMETRY */}\n          {activeTab === \"telemetry\" && (\n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              \n              {/* BENTO GRID OF SYSTEM TELEMETRY */}\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                \n                {/* 1. Core Sovereignty Block */}\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-2 font-mono\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40\">Partition Scope</span>\n                    <Cpu className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5 text-xs text-white/70\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Tier Level:</span><span className=\"text-amber-300 font-bold uppercase\">{client.tier}</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Enclave Region:</span><span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">{client.region}</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Isolated Domain:</span><span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">{client.domain}</span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 2. Compute Allocation Block */}\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-2 font-mono\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40\">Hardware Allotment</span>\n                    <HardDrive className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5 text-xs text-white/70\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Secure CPU loops:</span><span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">128 Threads</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Isolation Enclave:</span><span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">AMD SEV-SNP (Sovereign)</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Active Memory:</span><span className=\"text-white font-mono\">512 GB ECC RAM</span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 3. SLA Security Assurance */}\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-2 font-mono\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40\">SLA & Bilaterals</span>\n                    <Clock className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5 text-xs text-white/70\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">ISO-27001 Status:</span><span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">CERTIFIED</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">SLA wire response:</span><span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">&lt; 15 Minute Dedicated</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Monthly limit:</span><span className=\"text-white\">1.5M Epoch credits</span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 4. Contact & Identity Boundary */}\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-2 font-mono\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] uppercase font-bold text-white/40\">Custodian Bounds</span>\n                    <Users className=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-400\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5 text-xs text-white/70\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Sovereign Owner:</span><span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{client.accountOwner}</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Contact Person:</span><span className=\"text-white/80\">{client.contactName}</span></div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\"><span className=\"text-white/30\">Contact Email:</span><span className=\"text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] truncate max-w-[140px]\">{client.contactEmail}</span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n              {/* ACTIVE PROJECTS TABLE */}\n              <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                    <Layers className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Active Grids ({clientProjects.length})</h3>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono\">Continuous compliance active</span>\n                </div>\n\n                {clientProjects.length === 0 ? (\n                  <div className=\"text-center py-6 text-white/40 text-xs font-mono\">\n                    No active sandbox grids associated with this tenant partition.\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <div className=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                    <table className=\"w-full text-left border-collapse font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                      <thead>\n                        <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 text-white/40\">\n                          <th className=\"pb-2\">Grid ID / Name</th>\n                          <th className=\"pb-2\">Enclave Type</th>\n                          <th className=\"pb-2 text-center\">Nodes</th>\n                          <th className=\"pb-2 text-right\">Status</th>\n                        </tr>\n                      </thead>\n                      <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-white/[0.03]\">\n                        {clientProjects.map((proj) => (\n                          <tr key={proj.id} className=\"text-white/80\">\n                            <td className=\"py-2.5\">\n                              <div className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">{proj.name}</div>\n                              <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-[#009DFF]\">{proj.id.toUpperCase()}</div>\n                            </td>\n                            <td className=\"py-2.5 text-white/60\">{proj.enclaveType}</td>\n                            <td className=\"py-2.5 text-center text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">{proj.nodesCount} Cores</td>\n                            <td className=\"py-2.5 text-right\">\n                              <span className=\"inline-flex rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[8.5px] font-bold bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/20 uppercase\">\n                                {proj.status}\n                              </span>\n                            </td>\n                          </tr>\n                        ))}\n                      </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n          {/* TAB CONTENT: SVG ENCLAVE ARCHITECTURE GRAPHIC */}\n          {activeTab === \"architecture\" && (\n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              \n              <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">HSM Airgap Boundary & Key-Exchange Topology</h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/40 font-mono\">\n                    Deterministic visual model of {client.name.replace(\" [Preview Client]\", \"\")}'s hardware-locked enclave isolation loops and live attestation pathways.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* CUSTOM SVG/CSS ENCLAVE DIAGRAM */}\n                <div className=\"relative w-full h-[260px] bg-black/60 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\">\n                  \n                  {/* Subtle Grid Background */}\n                  <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.015)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.015)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:16px_16px]\" />\n                  \n                  {/* Radial spotlight */}\n                  <div className=\"absolute w-[200px] h-[200px] rounded-full bg-[#009DFF]/5 blur-[60px]\" />\n\n                  {/* Bespoke Dynamic SVG Architecture Graphic */}\n                  <svg className=\"relative w-full h-full max-w-[500px]\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 260\">\n                    <defs>\n                      <linearGradient id=\"laser-grad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0%\">\n                        <stop offset=\"0%\" stopColor=\"#00FFC2\" stopOpacity=\"0.2\" />\n                        <stop offset=\"50%\" stopColor=\"#00FFC2\" stopOpacity=\"1\" />\n                        <stop offset=\"100%\" stopColor=\"#00FFC2\" stopOpacity=\"0.2\" />\n                      </linearGradient>\n                      <linearGradient id=\"hsm-blue-grad\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                        <stop offset=\"0%\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" stopOpacity=\"0.3\" />\n                        <stop offset=\"100%\" stopColor=\"#004e80\" stopOpacity=\"0.05\" />\n                      </linearGradient>\n                    </defs>\n\n                    {/* Laser Path 1 (Attestation Pulse) */}\n                    <path \n                      d=\"M 90 130 C 180 60, 320 60, 410 130\" \n                      fill=\"none\" \n                      stroke=\"url(#laser-grad)\" \n                      strokeWidth=\"2\"\n                      strokeDasharray=\"15 85\"\n                      className=\"animate-[dash_4s_linear_infinite]\"\n                      style={{\n                        animation: \"dash 4s linear infinite\"\n                      }}\n                    />\n\n                    {/* Laser Path 2 (Data Boundary Loop) */}\n                    <path \n                      d=\"M 90 130 C 180 200, 320 200, 410 130\" \n                      fill=\"none\" \n                      stroke=\"#009DFF\" \n                      strokeWidth=\"1.5\"\n                      strokeOpacity=\"0.4\"\n                      strokeDasharray=\"6 6\"\n                    />\n\n                    {/* Laser Pulse along path 2 */}\n                    <circle r=\"3\" fill=\"#009DFF\">\n                      <animateMotion dur=\"3s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" path=\"M 90 130 C 180 200, 320 200, 410 130\" />\n                    </circle>\n\n                    {/* Central Sovereign Enclave Node */}\n                    <g transform=\"translate(250, 130)\">\n                      {/* Pulse Circle */}\n                      <circle r=\"34\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00FFC2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\">\n                        <animate attributeName=\"r\" values=\"34;48;34\" dur=\"3s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                        <animate attributeName=\"stroke-opacity\" values=\"0.2;0;0.2\" dur=\"3s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                      </circle>\n                      \n                      {/* Hexagon Outer */}\n                      <polygon \n                        points=\"0,-28 24,-14 24,14 0,28 -24,14 -24,-14\" \n                        fill=\"url(#hsm-blue-grad)\" \n                        stroke=\"#00FFC2\" \n                        strokeWidth=\"2\" \n                        className=\"animate-pulse\"\n                      />\n                      \n                      {/* Central core icon mapping (Lock) */}\n                      <circle r=\"12\" fill=\"#030303\" stroke=\"#00FFC2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                      <path d=\"M -4 -2 L -4 4 L 4 4 L 4 -2 Z M -2.5 -2 L -2.5 -4 C -2.5 -5 -1.5 -5.5 0 -5.5 C 1.5 -5.5 2.5 -5 2.5 -4 L 2.5 -2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00FFC2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeLinecap=\"round\" />\n                      \n                      <text y=\"42\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#00FFC2\" fontSize=\"9\" fontWeight=\"bold\" fontFamily=\"monospace\">HSM_CORE</text>\n                    </g>\n\n                    {/* Left Node: Decapsulated TLS Port */}\n                    <g transform=\"translate(90, 130)\">\n                      <circle r=\"18\" fill=\"#050505\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                      <circle r=\"4\" fill=\"#009DFF\" className=\"animate-ping\" />\n                      <path d=\"M -5 -5 L 5 5 M 5 -5 L -5 5\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                      <text y=\"-25\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.6\" fontSize=\"8\" fontWeight=\"bold\" fontFamily=\"monospace\">TLS_SOCKET</text>\n                      <text y=\"30\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#009DFF\" fontSize=\"8\" fontWeight=\"bold\" fontFamily=\"monospace\">eBPF BOUNDARY</text>\n                    </g>\n\n                    {/* Right Node: Multi-Agent Sandbox */}\n                    <g transform=\"translate(410, 130)\">\n                      <circle r=\"18\" fill=\"#050505\" stroke=\"#a855f7\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                      <rect x=\"-6\" y=\"-6\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#a855f7\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" className=\"animate-spin\" style={{ transformOrigin: \"0 0\" }} />\n                      <text y=\"-25\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.6\" fontSize=\"8\" fontWeight=\"bold\" fontFamily=\"monospace\">AGENT_LATTICE</text>\n                      <text y=\"30\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#a855f7\" fontSize=\"8\" fontWeight=\"bold\" fontFamily=\"monospace\">SECURE RING_3</text>\n                    </g>\n\n                  </svg>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Diagram Legend */}\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-[10px] text-white/40 pt-2 font-mono\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-start gap-2 p-2.5 rounded bg-black/20 border border-white/5\">\n                    <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#00FFC2] mt-1 shrink-0 animate-pulse\" />\n                    <div>\n                      <div className=\"font-bold text-white/70\">HSM Core Shield</div>\n                      <p className=\"leading-relaxed\">Physical hardware-locked security module validating real-time integrity certificates.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"flex items-start gap-2 p-2.5 rounded bg-black/20 border border-white/5\">\n                    <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] mt-1 shrink-0\" />\n                    <div>\n                      <div className=\"font-bold text-white/70\">eBPF Decapsulation Port</div>\n                      <p className=\"leading-relaxed\">Kernel-enforced zero-trust network boundary mapping dedicated telemetry sockets.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"flex items-start gap-2 p-2.5 rounded bg-black/20 border border-white/5\">\n                    <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#a855f7] mt-1 shrink-0\" />\n                    <div>\n                      <div className=\"font-bold text-white/70\">Agent Ring-3 Lattice</div>\n                      <p className=\"leading-relaxed\">Isolated compute sandbox running decapsulated LLM agents without external network exposure.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n          {/* TAB CONTENT: CONTINUOUS COMPLIANCE AUDIT */}\n          {activeTab === \"compliance\" && (\n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              \n              <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-5\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                    <ShieldCheck className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400\" />\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Continuous Alignment Verification</h3>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-mono font-bold uppercase bg-emerald-500/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-500/20\">ISO-27001 ACTIVE</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 font-mono leading-relaxed\">\n                  Below is the real-time continuous attestation checklist running within the target partition. All checks are processed inside secure hardware loops.\n                </p>\n\n                {/* COMPLIANCE CHRONOLOGY TIMELINE */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-xs\">\n                  \n                  {/* Step 1 */}\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center\">\n                      <div className=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-bold text-[10px]\">\n                        01\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"w-px h-10 bg-white/10\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5 pt-0.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">PKI Certificate Handshake</span>\n                        <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" />\n                      </div>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Root HSM signature authenticated and locked against client namespace cert.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Step 2 */}\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center\">\n                      <div className=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-bold text-[10px]\">\n                        02\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"w-px h-10 bg-white/10\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5 pt-0.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">eBPF Kernel Boundary Check</span>\n                        <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" />\n                      </div>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Verified kernel namespaces. Cryptographic memory isolation levels confirmed.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Step 3 */}\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center\">\n                      <div className=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-bold text-[10px]\">\n                        03\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"w-px h-10 bg-white/10\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5 pt-0.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">Zero-Trust Agent Ring Isolation</span>\n                        <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" />\n                      </div>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Continuous scanning confirmed zero model weight or contextual leakage outside secure boundary.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Step 4 */}\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center\">\n                      <div className=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 font-bold text-[10px] animate-pulse\">\n                        04\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5 pt-0.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">Attestation Ledger Seal</span>\n                        <span className=\"inline-flex rounded px-1 py-0.2 text-[8px] font-bold bg-blue-500/15 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/20 uppercase animate-pulse\">\n                          LIVE POLLING\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Continuous administrative telemetry sealed on epoch ledger index. SHA integrity signed.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n          {/* TAB CONTENT: ACTIVE WORKLOADS (AGENTS) */}\n          {activeTab === \"workloads\" && (\n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              \n              <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                    <Bot className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#a855f7]\" />\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Multi-Agent Sandbox Workloads</h3>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono\">Monitored ring allocation</span>\n                </div>\n\n                {clientAgents.length === 0 ? (\n                  <div className=\"text-center py-8 border border-dashed border-white/10 rounded-lg text-white/40 space-y-2 font-mono\">\n                    <Bot className=\"w-8 h-8 mx-auto opacity-35\" />\n                    <div>No Active LLM Agent Instances</div>\n                    <p className=\"text-[10px] max-w-xs mx-auto\">\n                      No live autonomous model workloads are executing inside this partition's secure memory boundary.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-xs\">\n                    {clientAgents.map((agent) => (\n                      <div \n                        key={agent.id}\n                        className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-3\"\n                      >\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-[10.5px] font-bold text-white uppercase\">{agent.name}</span>\n                            <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30\">{agent.id.toUpperCase()}</div>\n                          </div>\n                          <span className={`inline-flex rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[8.5px] font-bold border uppercase ${\n                            agent.status === \"active\" \n                              ? \"bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border-emerald-500/20\" \n                              : \"bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border-amber-500/20\"\n                          }`}>\n                            {agent.status}\n                          </span>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-[10px] text-white/50 pb-2 border-b border-white/5\">\n                          <div>Threads Allotted: <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{agent.threads} Cores</span></div>\n                          <div>Enclave Memory: <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{agent.memory}</span></div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                          <div className=\"text-[8.5px] text-white/30 uppercase font-bold flex items-center gap-1\">\n                            <Terminal className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                            <span>eBPF Telemetry Decapsulation Logs</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded bg-black/60 border border-white/5 font-mono text-[9px] text-emerald-400/80 space-y-1.5 max-h-[100px] overflow-y-auto\">\n                            {agent.logs.map((log, index) => (\n                              <div key={index} className=\"truncate\">&gt; {log}</div>\n                            ))}\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                      </div>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n        </div>\n\n        {/* RIGHT COLUMN: ADMINISTRATIVE UTILITIES & REAL-TIME LOGS */}\n        <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n          \n          {/* ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS UTILITY BOX */}\n          <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <Settings2 className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Administrative Actions</h3>\n            </div>\n            \n            <p className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/40 font-mono leading-relaxed\">\n              Execute low-level partition management utilities. All actions undergo cryptographic logging.\n            </p>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-3 font-mono text-xs\">\n              \n              {/* Action 1: Rotate HSM Seal */}\n              <button\n                onClick={handleRotateHSMSeal}\n                disabled={isRotatingKey || isScanning}\n                className={`w-full h-10 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                  isRotatingKey ? \"bg-[#00FFC2]/5 text-[#00FFC2] border-[#00FFC2]/20\" : \"bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <RefreshCw className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2] ${isRotatingKey ? \"animate-spin\" : \"\"}`} />\n                <span>{isRotatingKey ? \"Rotating Keys...\" : \"Rotate HSM Seal Keys\"}</span>\n              </button>\n\n              {/* Action 2: Run Boundary Scan */}\n              <button\n                onClick={handleRunSecurityScan}\n                disabled={isRotatingKey || isScanning}\n                className={`w-full h-10 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer transition-all ${\n                  isScanning ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF]/20\" : \"bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <Shield className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF] ${isScanning ? \"animate-pulse\" : \"\"}`} />\n                <span>{isScanning ? \"Scanning Boundaries...\" : \"Run Kernel Boundary Scan\"}</span>\n              </button>\n\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[9.5px] text-white/30 leading-relaxed bg-white/[0.01] p-3 rounded border border-white/5 font-mono\">\n              <AlertTriangle className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n              <span>\n                WARNING: Provisioning alterations bypass standard tenant-side locks. Proceed under ISO-27001 oversight.\n              </span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* TELEMETRY CONSOLE HUD */}\n          <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-3 flex flex-col h-[280px]\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                <Terminal className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400\" />\n                <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Oversight Console</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-ping\" />\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"flex-1 bg-black/50 border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3 font-mono text-[9.5px] text-emerald-400/85 space-y-2 overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden select-text text-left\">\n              {consoleLogs.map((log, index) => (\n                <div key={index} className=\"leading-relaxed break-all\">\n                  {log}\n                </div>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}","insert_line":null}}}
